            <title>[CASSANDRA-9510] assassinating an unknown endpoint could npe</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CASSANDRA-9510</link>
                <project id="12310865" key="CASSANDRA">Apache Cassandra</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;If the code assissinates an unknown endpoint, it doesn&apos;t generate a &apos;tokens&apos; collection, which then does&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;epState.addApplicationState(ApplicationState.STATUS, StorageService.instance.valueFactory.left(tokens, computeExpireTime()));&lt;/p&gt;

